s will help you to choose the best plan according to your needs. Note that we can also arrange a custom plan specially for you.\n<h4>All in one place</h4>\nYes, we have it all - Diary products, Meat, Bread, Drinks, Eggs and more![/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="More Than 15 Years In The Business"][vc_column_text]\n<h4>Almost 16!</h4>\nWe are working with farms and organic products for almost 16 years and to be honest this is the best job ever - to see the people smiles when they try our tasty berries or fresh milk!\n<h4>100% Professionals</h4>\nWe have contracts with major organizations from in and out of the country. We have received the Best Organic Food of The Year Award 2013.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1409971403713{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;background-color: #f2f2f2 !important;}" parallax_speed="0.1" bg_video_transparent="0" animation="bottom-to-top" type="ww-default"][vc_column width="1/1"][title title="Latest News" align="text-center" underline="1"][ww-shortcode-carousel-post styles="style-1-organicfood" crop_image="1" rows="1" same_height="1" show_nav="1" show_date="1" show_description="1" read_more="More" posts_per_page="12" orderby="date" order="DESC" category="" width_image="288" height_image="154" post_type="post" show_title="1" testimonial_styles="style-1-consilium" client_styles="style-1" produce_styles="style-1" show_info="1" margin_item="20" nav_postion="text-right" nav_position="text-center" excerpt_length="10"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1412160658317{border-top-width: 1px !important;border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 35px !important;padding-bottom: 65px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.1" bg_video_transparent="0" type="ww-default"][vc_column width="1/1"][title title="6 Steps 2 A Longer Life" align="text-center" underline="1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inne