kberries.\r\n\r\nPeter: Did you breed any animals?\r\n\r\nHershel: Yes, we have pigs, cows - from which we get the best organic milk :) ...we have also chickens.[/vc_column_text][vc_button title="Read The Whole Interview" color="btn-primary"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="88" img_size="medium" alignment="center"][vc_column_text]Hershel Green - farmer from Vermont[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row animation="bottom-to-top" parallax_speed="0.1" css=".vc_custom_1409971595937{margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 35px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" bg_video_transparent="0"][vc_column][title title="Organic-Bio Labels" align="text-center" underline="1"][ww-shortcode-carousel-post post_type="myclients" show_nav="1" nav_position="text-right" show_tooltip="1"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2361-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-01-01 12:43:46', '2017-01-01 12:43:46', '', 2361, 'http://localhost/mmn/2017/01/01/2361-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
